        <form action="/listSpecies" method="get">

        <form action="/karyotype" method="get">

            <p><button type="submit">Send</button></p><br>
         </form>

        <p>3)Chromosome Length</p>
        <form action="/chromosomeLength" method="get">
            <p>Select the species: <input type="text" name="specie"></p>
            <p>Select a chromosome: <input type="text" name="chromo"></p>
            <p>Select to retrieve json: <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"></p>
            <p><button type="submit">Send</button></p><br>
        </form>

        <p>4)Sequence of a given human gene</p>
        <form action="/geneSeq" method="get">
            <p>Introduce the name of a gene: <input type="text" name="gene"></p>
            <p>Select to retrieve json: <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"></p>
            <p><button type="submit">Send</button></p><br>
        </form>

        <p>5)Information about a human gene</p>
        <form action="/geneInfo" method="get">
            <p>Introduce the name of a gene: <input type="text" name="gene"></p>
            <p>Select to retrieve json: <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"></p>
            <p><button type="submit">Send</button></p><br>
         </form>

        <p>6)Calculations on the given human gene</p>
        <form action="/geneCalc" method="get">
            <p>Introduce the name of a gene: <input type="text" name="gene"></p>
            <p>Select to retrieve json: <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"></p>
            <p><button type="submit">Send</button></p><br>
        </form>

        <p>7)Names of the genes located in the chromosome from the start to end positions</p>
        <form action="/geneList" method="get">
            <p>Introduce the number of a chromosome: <input type="text" name="chromo"></p>
            <p>Introduce the start position: <input type="number" name="start" min="0"></p>
            <p>Introduce the end position: <input type="number" name="end" min="0"></p>
            <p>Select to retrieve json: <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"></p>
            <p><button type="submit">Send</button></p><br>
        </form>
